---
title: Italian Pork Parmigiana with Carrot Ribbon & Apple Salad
description: Who doesn’t love a good parmigiana? Baked in a thick gooey layer of Cheddar cheese, this tomato coated and golden crumbed pork
will definitely be the star of the evening. Take it to new levels by swapping out your usual side of fries with a fresh and crunchy salad.
